## Pricing

I believe in transparent pricing. For a detailed breakdown of what SEO consulting costs and what influences the investment, read my guide on [how much SEO costs](/services/how-much-does-seo-cost/).

As a general guide:

- **One-off technical audit** — From £750. A comprehensive review with a prioritised roadmap.
- **Monthly retainer** — From £800/month. Ongoing strategy, implementation support, and reporting.
- **Project-based work** — Priced individually. Content strategy builds, topical authority mapping, or site migration support.

Every engagement starts with a clear scope and agreed deliverables. There are no hidden fees, no long-term lock-ins, and no surprises.

